### Romani Bible: Romans

<span id="an_1:1">1:1</span> O Pavlo, ek sluga le Jesus Kristosko, sas
akhardo te avel Apostle alosardo te phenel e lashi viasta le Devleski.

<span id="an_1:2">1:2</span> E lashi viasta kai sas shinadi mai anglal
katar O Del katar leske profeturia kai si ande Vorba le Devleski.

<span id="an_1:3">1:3</span> Kai mothol pa pesko Shav O Jesus Kristo,
kai kerdilo andai vitsa le Davidoski ando stato.

<span id="an_1:4">1:4</span> Ai sas thodino Shav Devlesko putierasa pala
Swunto Duxo, ai katar lesko zhuvindimos mashkar le mule.

<span id="an_1:5">1:5</span> O Jesus Kristo amaro Del kai lestar sas ame
te avas apostluria, ando anav le Kristosko, te anas manushen ande sa le
thema te pachanpe ai te keren o zakono le Devlesko.

<span id="an_1:6">1:6</span> Vi tume kai san ande Rome, kai O Del
akhardia tume te aven le Jesus Kristoske.

<span id="an_1:7">1:7</span> Ramov tumenge, tumenge kai san ande Rome,
tume savorhe kai O Del drago tumenge, ai akhardia te traiin leske, te
del tume o lashimos ai e pacha katar amaro Del, amaro Dat, ai O Del
Jesus Kristo.

<span id="an_1:8">1:8</span> Mai anglal naisisarav murhe Devleske ando
Jesus Kristo pa tumende, ke ashunas ke den duma pa tumaro pachamos ande
sa e lumia.

<span id="an_1:9">1:9</span> O Del kai me kerav leske buchi sa murhe
ilesa, kai phenav e lashi viasta pa lesko Shav, zhanel ke da ma sagda
goji tumende.

<span id="an_1:10">1:10</span> Ai mangav sagda ando murho rhugimos, te
avel ma dino katar leske voia o raduimos te zhav te dikhav tume.

<span id="an_1:11">1:11</span> Ke mangav te dikhav tume, te anav tumenge
iek podarka katar O Swunto Duxo, te aven zurale.

<span id="an_1:12">1:12</span> Ai mangav mai but te avav tumende te las
andek than iek zor, me katar tumaro pachamos, ai tume katar murho
pachamos.

<span id="an_1:13">1:13</span> Chi mangav te mekav tumen bi te zhanen
murhe phral, ke butivar manglem te zhav te dikhav tumen, numa
aterdiarenas ma zhi akana, ke mangavas murhi buchi te kerel mishtimos
mashkar tumende, sar kerdilia mashkar le kolaver thema anda lumia.

<span id="an_1:14">1:14</span> Ke trobul te zhav kal manush kai traiin
andel foruria ai vi kal manush kai si avrial, ai vi kal gojaver ai vi
kodola kai nai gojaver.

<span id="an_1:15">1:15</span> Anda kodia sima ando ilo te phenav
tumenge e lashi viasta, vi tumenge kai san ande Rome.

<span id="an_1:16">1:16</span> Ke chi lazhav katar Vorba le Kristoski;
ke kodia si e putiera le Devleski ai o skepimos kodoleske kai pachalpe;
mai anglal o Zhidovo, porme o Greko.

<span id="an_1:17">1:17</span> Ke ande Vorba le Devleski si o chachimos
le Devlesko katar o pachamos ai le pachamaske, ke kadia si le ramome, o
manush kai si vorta le Devlesa traiila anda pachamos.

<span id="an_1:18">1:18</span> O Del sikavel peski xoli anda cheri pe sa
o bezex ai so godi baio keren le manush, ai katar o bezex kai keren te
aterdiaren o chachimos.

<span id="an_1:19">1:19</span> O Del dosharel le ke so zhanen katar O
Del, nai trutno lenge te haliaren. O Del sikadia lenge sar si.

<span id="an_1:20">1:20</span> Chaches de sar O Del kerdia e lumia, le
bucha kai wo kerel ai ame chi dikhas, kodia si leski putiera kai shoxar
chi getolpe, ai wo kai si Swunto dikhel pe andel dieli kai kerdia, ai
kadia le manush sai zhanen so kerdia, saxke te na mothon ke chi zhanen!

<span id="an_1:21">1:21</span> Zhanen le Devles, numa chi luvudin les,
ai chi naisin leske sar trobul te kerel pe le Devleske, numa won lenge
ginduria kerdile dzilimos, ai lengo ilo zurailo ai pherdilo tuniariko.

<span id="an_1:22">1:22</span> Won mothon ke gojaver le, numa dzile le.

<span id="an_1:23">1:23</span> Kai trobul te luvudin o barimos le
Devlesko kai chi merel, numa won luvudin xoxamne ikoni kai miazon
manushen kai sai meren, ai ka chiriklia, ai zhigeni shtare punrhensa, ai
sapen, ai shupolen.

<span id="an_1:24">1:24</span> Anda kodia O Del meklia le te keren dieli
bi vuzhe, ke lengo ilo mangelas kadia, ai traiinas defial zhungales iek
kavresa.

<span id="an_1:25">1:25</span> Won kai parhude o chachimos le Devlesko
ando xoxaimos, ai luvudisarde ai podaisarde le manushes de sar kodoles
kai kerdia les, ai kai si Swuntsome sagda. Amen.

<span id="an_1:26">1:26</span> Anda kodia O Del meklia le te keren dieli
zhungale, vi lenge zhuvlia parhude, ai chi mai keren so sas malades, ai
keren dieli kai si bi malade:

<span id="an_1:27">1:27</span> Vi le mursh, chi mai keren so trobulas te
kerdiol le zhuvliansa, ai te aven drago iek avreske, le mursh keren
dieli zhungale iek avresa, ai kadia doshale le kai rimonpe katar O Del.

<span id="an_1:28">1:28</span> Chi mangle te luvudin le Devles, O Del
meklia le pala pengi goji, kai nai vorta te keren so chi trobulas te
keren.

<span id="an_1:29">1:29</span> Pherdo xoxaimos le, kurvisia, chorho
ginduria, bi lashe, ai mangen so si avres, ai pherdo zhaluzile ai
mudaren, ai keren chingara, maren mui iek avesa, ai atsaren, ai roden
baio, ai pupuin,

<span id="an_1:30">1:30</span> ai mothon bi lashimos pa iek avreske, won
si le duzhmaia le Devleske, dziliaren, barimatange, mothon so kerde won
ai won keren dieli te xoxaven, ai te keren baio, ai chi keren so mangen
o dat ai e dei lendar ai chi pachan lengo mui,

<span id="an_1:31">1:31</span> Chi haliaren kanch, ai chi keren so
mothon, bi lashe le ai nai le dragostia, bi malako le kolavrenge:

<span id="an_1:32">1:32</span> Zhanen o zakono le Devlesko, le manush
kai keren kadia trobul mudarde, numa savon keren kadala bucha, ai mai
but mothon ke vorta keren kadala kai keren sar lende.

<span id="an_2:1">2:1</span> Tu kai keres kris pel kolaver chi san
iertime; kon godi avesa ke kana keres kris pel kolaver, ai vi tu keres
sa kodola dieli, tu korkorho keres kris pe tute.

<span id="an_2:2">2:2</span> Ke zhanas ke O Del kerel kris vorta ai
chachi pe kodola kai keren kodolendar dieli.

<span id="an_2:3">2:3</span> Tu gindis ke skepisar katar e kris le
Devleski, tu kai keres kris pe kodola kai keren kadala dieli, kana vi tu
keres sar lende?

<span id="an_2:4">2:4</span> Vai tu, nai tuke drago o lashimos le
Devlesko kai azhukerel ai rhevdil; tu chi zhanes ke o lashimos le
Devlesko trobul te parhuvel cho traio.

<span id="an_2:5">2:5</span> Numa zuralo cho ilo, chi manges te
parhudios anda kodia, tu lashares tuke kris mai bari kana avela o dies,
kai O Del sikavela peski xoli ai peski kris kai si chachi.

<span id="an_2:6">2:6</span> Ai kai O Del dela sakones pala so kerdia.

<span id="an_2:7">2:7</span> Dela o traio kai chi mai getolpe kodolen
kai roden te keren o mishtimos, ai roden o barimos ai o luvudimos, ai o
traio kai chi merel.

<span id="an_2:8">2:8</span> Numa sikavela xoliariko zurales pe kodola
kai xoliavon pe leste, ai chi keren o chachimos, numa keren le chorhe
dieli,

<span id="an_2:9">2:9</span> O chino ai o nekazo avela pe kodola kai
keren o baio; pel Zhiduvuria mai anglal, numa vi pe kodola kai nai
Zhiduvuria.

<span id="an_2:10">2:10</span> Numa O Del dela o barimos, ai o
luvudimos, ai e pacha kodolenge kai keren o lashimos; kal Zhiduvuria mai
anglal, numa vi ka kodola kai Nai Zhiduvuria.

<span id="an_2:11">2:11</span> Ke le Devleske savorhe iek fialuri.

<span id="an_2:12">2:12</span> Kodola kai keren bezexa bi te zhanen o
zakono le Mosesosko xasavona bi le zakonosko; numa kodola kai keren
bezexa ai zhanen o zakono avena dine pe kris pala zakono kai zhanen.

<span id="an_2:13">2:13</span> Ke le manush kai si drago le Devleske,
nai kodola kai ferdi ashunen o zakono, numa kodola kai keren so mothol o
zakone.

<span id="an_2:14">2:14</span> Kana kodola kai Nai Zhiduvuria, kai chi
zhanen o zakono le Zhidovongo, keren anda pende so mothol o zakono, si
le iek zakono lenge, marka ke nai le o zakono.

<span id="an_2:15">2:15</span> Sikaven kadia, ke sar trobul te keres kai
si phendo, katar e kris ramome ande lenge ile. Lengo ilo sikavel lenge,
vi ke lenge ginduria kai univar kerel kris pe lende, ai univar chacharel
le.

<span id="an_2:16">2:16</span> Eta, so sikadiola o dies kai O Del dela
pe kris katar o Kristo, so godi si garado andel traiuria le manushenge
ai sar mothol e lashi viasta le Devleski kai me mothav.

<span id="an_2:17">2:17</span> Numa tu des tu o anav Zhidovo, inkerdios
katar o zakono, ai barimata keres che Devlesa,

<span id="an_2:18">2:18</span> zhanes e voia le Devleski, ai o zakono
sichardia tu, te alos so si mishto;

<span id="an_2:19">2:19</span> tu gindis ke sai sikaves o drom le
korhenge, ai sai aves iek vediara kodolenge kai si ando tuniariko,

<span id="an_2:20">2:20</span> tu sichares kodolen kai chi zhanen, ai
sichares le ternen pa Del, ke tu zhanes ke o zakono sikavel vorta so si,
o chachimos ai zhanglimos.

<span id="an_2:21">2:21</span> Apo, tu kai sichares le kolavren, sostar
chi sichares tu tut? Tu kai mothos ke chi trobul te chores, sostar tu
chores?

<span id="an_2:22">2:22</span> Tu kai mothos ke chi trobul te phires
pala kolavreski rhomni. Sostar tu keres kurvimos? Tu kai nai tuke drago
le ikoni, Sostar chores andal tampluria?

<span id="an_2:23">2:23</span> Barimata keres ke si tu o zakono, numa
nai tuke lazhav katar O Del kai keres so mothol o zakono te na keres.

<span id="an_2:24">2:24</span> Ke E Vorba le Devleski mothol, pala
tumende le Zhiduvuria o kolaver narodo mothol nasulimos pa Del.

<span id="an_2:25">2:25</span> Te keresa so mothol o zakono, o semno nai
intaino, numa te na keresa so mothol o zakono, kadia si sar te na
avilino semno pe tute.

<span id="an_2:26">2:26</span> Ai o manush kai nas semno pe leste (nai
Zhidovo), kerel o zakono sar lende ai kerel so phenel o zakono, O Del
gindil pa leste sar ek Zhidovo.

<span id="an_2:27">2:27</span> O manush kai nai semno pe leste ando
stato kerel o zakono solaxasa, numa tu kai san ek Zhidovo chi keres o
zakono, marka ke si tu o zakono ramome, ai ke te san semnosa.

<span id="an_2:28">2:28</span> Chaches, o chacho Zhidovo nai ferdi kodo
kai miazol, ai kai si semnome kai dichol avrial o stato,

<span id="an_2:29">2:29</span> numa o chacho Zhidovo si kodo kai si
andral, ai kan si semno ande lesko ilo, iek semno kai avel katar O
Swunto Duxo le Devlesko, ai na katar o zakono kai si ramome, o chacho
Zhidovo avel lesko barimos na katar le manush, numa katar O Del.

<span id="an_3:1">3:1</span> So mai niris te aves Zhidovo, o semno mai
nai kanchi? But si te niris ande soste godi!

<span id="an_3:2">3:2</span> Ai mai anglal kal Zhiduvuria O Del meklia
kado divano.

<span id="an_3:3">3:3</span> Apo, so te mothos te sas mashkar lende kai
chi kerde o zakono, O Del si te mekel le ke won mekle les?

<span id="an_3:4">3:4</span> Nichi! Trobul O Del te kerel buchi le
chachimasa, marka te avela swako manush xoxamlo, sar mothol E Vorba le
Devleski, trobul te arakhen ke vorta sam ande so mothos; ai te niris
kana den tu pe kris.

<span id="an_3:5">3:5</span> Numa o bezex kai keres si te sikavel ke O
Del vorta lo, so mothas ame? O Del nai vorta ke dosharel ame? Dav duma
sar den duma le manush.

<span id="an_3:6">3:6</span> Nichi! Ke O Del te na avilino vorta, sar
sai del pe kris la lumia?

<span id="an_3:7">3:7</span> Ai pala murho xoxaimos o chachimos le
Devlesko sikadiol mai but pe lesko barimos; sostar te mai avav jindo sar
iek bezexalo?

<span id="an_3:8">3:8</span> Ai porme, sostar te na mothas, "Keras o bi
lashimos saxke te anklel o lashimas." Chaches uni mothon bi lashimos pa
mande ai dosharel ma ke sostar mothav, 'Kodola manush avena doshale sar
trobul pe.'"

<span id="an_3:9">3:9</span> Numa sam ame le Zhiduvuria mai lashe sar le
kolaver manush? Nichi! Ke vunzhe phendem ke le Zhiduvuria ai le kolaver
manush iek fialo le, ai savorhe bezexale le.

<span id="an_3:10">3:10</span> Sar si ramome ande Vorba le Devleski,
"Nai chi iek manush kai si vorta, nai, chi iek.

<span id="an_3:11">3:11</span> Chi iek kai haliarel, khonik chi rodel le
Devles (Ps 14:2).

<span id="an_3:12">3:12</span> Savorhe xasarde le katar O Del; ai
xasaile, nai chi iek kai kerel o mishtimos, chi iek.

<span id="an_3:13">3:13</span> Lenge kox si sar iek grepoäevo phuterdo,
lenge shib si kai xoxaven lasa, le vorbi kai anklen anda lengo vursh si
sar e votrava le sapesko; (Ps 5:9, 140:3).

<span id="an_3:14">3:14</span> Lengo mui pherdo bi vuzhimos ai den
armaia.

<span id="an_3:15">3:15</span> Nashen zurales te mudaren:

<span id="an_3:16">3:16</span> Ai katar godi nakhen, phagaven ai keren
baio:

<span id="an_3:17">3:17</span> Chi zhanen o drom la pachako,

<span id="an_3:18">3:18</span> Nai dar le Devleski angla lenge iakha.

<span id="an_3:19">3:19</span> Zhanas ke so godi mothol o zakono, mothol
les kodolenge kai si tela zakono, saxke swako mui te avel phandado, ai
sa e lumia te avel arakhli doshali angla Del.

<span id="an_3:20">3:20</span> Ke khonik chi avela arakho vorta angla
Del ke kerdia so motholas o zakono; o zakono si ferdi te sikavel le
manusheske ke bezexalo lo.

<span id="an_3:21">3:21</span> Numa akana O Del sikadia amenge sar kerel
anda amende, vorta angla leste bi le zakonosko. o zakono ai le
profeturia phende sas pa kadia diela.

<span id="an_3:22">3:22</span> O Del kerel te aven le manush vorta ke
pachanpe ando Jesus Kristo. Ai kodia si sa kodolenge kai pachanpe ando
Kristo, ke angla Del savorhe iek fialo sam:

<span id="an_3:23">3:23</span> Ke savorhe bezexale le, ai dur si katar
lesko skepimos.

<span id="an_3:24">3:24</span> Numa O Del ande pesko lashimos kerel te
aven vorta ivia pala O Kristo Jesus, kai skepil le.

<span id="an_3:25">3:25</span> O Del thodia les po trushul, o iertimos
le bezexengo avel pala o rat le Kristosko kana pachanpe ande leste, O
Del manglia te sikavel sar pesko Shav O Jesus Kristo si chacho. Mai
anglal, azhukerelas ai chi kerelas baio le bezexalenge;

<span id="an_3:26">3:26</span> Numa akana O Del sikavel sar iertil le
bezexa le manushenge te aven vorta. Ke wo mangel te sikavel kai wo si
vorta, ai vi te kerel vorta anda sa kodola kai pachanpe ando Jesus.

<span id="an_3:27">3:27</span> Mai si, le manushen, voia te keren
barimata? Nichi, vov si! Si te keren so mothol o zakono? Nichi, Numa ke
pachanpe ando Kristo.

<span id="an_3:28">3:28</span> Ke ame gindisaras ke o manush vorta lo
pala pesko pachamos bi te kerel so mothol o zakono.

<span id="an_3:29">3:29</span> O Del si ferdi O Del le Zhidovongo? Nai
vi kodolengo kai Nai Zhiduvuria? E, wo si O Del kai Nai Zhiduvuria.

<span id="an_3:30">3:30</span> Ke ferdi iek Del si, kai kerela te aven
vorta pala pachamos le Zhiduvuria, ai vi kodola kai Nai Zhiduvuria.

<span id="an_3:31">3:31</span> Apo, akana chi mai keras o zakono ke pala
pachamos? Nichi, akana mai but te las ame.

<span id="an_4:1">4:1</span> Apo so te mothas, so lia o Abraham amaro
dat?

<span id="an_4:2">4:2</span> Te avilino o Abraham arakhlo vorta katar O
Del palal dieli kai kerdia, sai kerdino barimata, numa nashtil te kerel
barimata angla Del. Chaches E Vorba le Devleski mothol.

<span id="an_4:3">4:3</span> "O Abraham pachaiape ando Del, ai O Del
jinelas les vorta pala pesko pachamos."

<span id="an_4:4">4:4</span> O manush kai kerel buchi si les pochin;
kodia pochin nai jindi sar iek podarka ivia, numa kerdia buchi pala
late.

<span id="an_4:5">4:5</span> Numa kana iek manush bi te kerel buchi thol
ferdi pesko pachamos ando Del, ai O Del jinel vorta le bezexa leske, O
Del dikhel lesko pachamos te jinel les sar vorta angla leste.

<span id="an_4:6">4:6</span> Ai kadia si kai o David del duma pa
raduimos le manushesko, kai O Del jinel les vorta bi te lel sama so
kerel:

<span id="an_4:7">4:7</span> "Raduime te aven kodola kai O Del
iertisardia lenge shipki, ai kai iertisardia lenge bezexa. Raduime o
manush kai O Del chi jinel lesko bezex.

<span id="an_4:8">4:8</span> Kado mishtimos si ferdi le manushenge kai
si semno pe lende, vai vi le manushenge kai nai semno pe lende?

<span id="an_4:9">4:9</span> Akana so phendiam ke O Del jinel le
Abrahamos sa vorta, ke lel sama ka lesko pachamos." (Gen 15:6).

<span id="an_4:10">4:10</span> Kana kodia diela kerdili? Sas mai angla
vai mai palal kana Abraham sas semno pe leste? Nichi mai palal, numa mai
anglal.

<span id="an_4:11">4:11</span> O Abraham sas les dino o semno te dichol,
kodia sas o semno te sikavel ke O Del jinelas les sa vorta pala pesko
pachamos mai anglal sar te avel semno pe leste, o Abraham kai si o dat
sa kodolenge kai pachanpe ando Del, bi te aven semnome, kodia si kodola
kai nai ferdi ke si semnome, numa ke lenpe pala traio le pachamasko ke
sar amaro dat, o Abraham traiisardia mai anglal sar te avel semnome.

<span id="an_4:13">4:13</span> O Del shinadia le Abrahamoske ai
kodolenge kai aven pala leste ke e lumia avela lenge. Kodo shinaimos na
ke o Abraham kerdia o zakono, numa ke sas jindo sa vorta katar O Del
pala pesko pachamos.

<span id="an_4:14">4:14</span> Te avilino kodola kai keren o zakono
ferdi won te len so sas shinado. Apo o pachamos intaino lo, ai so sas
shinado katar O Del nas te mol kanch.

<span id="an_4:15">4:15</span> Ke o zakono anel e xoli le Devleski; Numa
kotse kai nai zakono, nai chi bezexa.

<span id="an_4:16">4:16</span> Anda kodia so sas shinado katar O Del sas
pala pachamos, saxke te avel ek podarka ivia katar O Del, ai te avel
lashi sas kodolenge kai avena katar o Abraham. Na ferdi kodolenge kai
keren o zakono, numa vi kodolenge kai pachanpe sar o Abraham pachaiape,
o Abraham si amaro dat savorhenge;

<span id="an_4:17">4:17</span> Sar mothol E Vorba le Devleski, "Kerdem
anda tute o dat bute themengo." Wo si amaro dat angla Del ande kodo kai
pachaiape, O Del kai del o traio le mulen, ai kerel te avel so nas
shoxar.

<span id="an_4:18">4:18</span> O Abraham pachaiape ai azhukerelas, kana
nas kanch te azhukerelas, ai kerdilo kadia "O dat bute themengo" Vorta
sar O Del phendiasas leske, 'Avela but narodo pala tute.'

<span id="an_4:19">4:19</span> Pashte iek shel bershengo sas; numa lesko
pachamos chi kovliolas kana delas pe goji ka pesko stato, kai sas vunzhe
sar mulo, ai e Sarah kai nashtilas te avel la glate.

<span id="an_4:20">4:20</span> Chi xasardo pesko pachamos, ai pachalaspe
ande so shinadiasas leske O Del; inker lesko pachamos bariolas, ai
naisilas le Devles.

<span id="an_4:21">4:21</span> Pachalaspe zurales ke O Del si les e
putiera te kerel so shinadia.

<span id="an_4:22">4:22</span> Anda kodia o Abraham pala pesko pachamos,
sas jindo vorta katar O Del.

<span id="an_4:23">4:23</span> Numa kadala vorbi "jindo sar vorta" nas
ferdi ramome leske,

<span id="an_4:24">4:24</span> Sas ramome vi amenge, ai iame sam jinde
sa vorta, ame kai pachas ande leste kai vazdia andai martia ka traio O
Jesus amaro Del.

<span id="an_4:25">4:25</span> Sas dino kai martia pala amare bezexa, ai
sas andino palpale ka traio amenge te kerel anda amende vorta angla Del.

<span id="an_5:1">5:1</span> Akana sam vorta angla Del pala pachamos, si
ame e pacha le Devlesa katar amaro Del Jesus Kristo.

<span id="an_5:2">5:2</span> Pala Jesus ai o pachamos kai si ame ande
leste, sai pashuas ka lashimos le Devlesko, ai kai akana beshas ande
kodia, ai so del ame o raduimos, si ke zhanas ke si ame than pasha
barimos le Devlesko.

<span id="an_5:3">5:3</span> Mai but raduisavas ande amaro chino, ke
zhanas ke pala chino sai porme azhukeras.

<span id="an_5:4">5:4</span> Kana sai azhukeres sai inkerdios kana avel
o zumaimos; ai ankeres, porme azhukeres.

<span id="an_5:5">5:5</span> Ai kodo azhukerimos nai intaino ke O Del
shordia peski dragostia ande amare ile le Swuntone Duxosa kai dia ame.

<span id="an_5:6">5:6</span> Inker kana nas ame zor, O Del mulo le
bezexalenge, e vriama kai sas thode katar O Del.

<span id="an_5:7">5:7</span> Trutno te merelpe ieke manusheske kai si
vorta. Amborim sai merel vari kon ieke manusheske kai si lasho.

<span id="an_5:8">5:8</span> Numa O Del sikadia amenge sode leske drago
amen; o Kristo mulo amenge kana inker samas bezexale!

<span id="an_5:9">5:9</span> Katar leski martia sam akana jinde vorta
angla Del; ai pala kodia avasa skepime lestar katar e xoli le Devleski.

<span id="an_5:10">5:10</span> Ame samas le duzhmaia le Devleske, numa
akana kerdia anda amende leske vortacha ke palai martia leske shaveske.
Akana mai but kai sam leske vortacha, avasa skepime pala traio lesko
shavesko.

<span id="an_5:11">5:11</span> Ai mai si mai but raduimos ando Del katar
amaro Del O Jesus Kristo, kai akana kerdia te avas le vortacha le
Devleske.

<span id="an_5:12">5:12</span> O bezex avilo ande lumia pala iek manush
o Adam; ai o bezex andia e martia; ai kadia e martia aresli sa le
manushen, ke savorhe kerde bezexa!

<span id="an_5:13">5:13</span> Mai anglal sar O Del dia o zakono ka
Moses o bezex vunzhe sas ande lumia; numa sar nas inker o zakono O Del
chi lelas sama le bezexeske.

<span id="an_5:14">5:14</span> Numa de katar e vriama le Adamoski zhi
kai e vriama le Mosesoski e martia sas, vi pel manush kai chi kerenas
bezexa sar o Adam kai dia opral pa so phendia leske.

<span id="an_5:15">5:15</span> Numa e shipka le Adamoski nai iek fialo.
Mai bari si e podarka le Devleski, kai del ame ivia. E, chaches si kai
but mule palai bezex ieke manusheske, numa o lashimos le Devlesko defial
mai barolo, ai e podarka kai dia ivia buten katar iek manush, O Jesus
Kristo.

<span id="an_5:16">5:16</span> Ai e podarka le Devleski nai sar o bezex
le ieke manushesko Adam. E kris kai avili pala bezex palai iek kerdia te
dosharel, numa e podarka dini ivia pala but shipke si te kerel o
skepimos.

<span id="an_5:17">5:17</span> E martia beshli ke palai shipka ieke
manusheski, numa katar iek O Jesus Kristo si ame mai but sa kolola kai
len but mishtimos katar O Del, ai podarka leski chachimaski traiina ai
avena pala kristo.

<span id="an_5:18">5:18</span> Sa kadia, e shipka le ieke manusheski o
Adam andia o xasarimos sa le manushengo; numa sakadia e buchi kodoleski
kai sas vorta O Jesus Kristo skepil sa le manushen katar e kris, ai del
le o traio.

<span id="an_5:19">5:19</span> Sakadia kai chi pachaia o mui kodo iek
manush kerdia anda but manush bezexale, ai sakadia pala iek manush kai
pachaia o mui, kerela anda but manush te aven vorta angla Del.

<span id="an_5:20">5:20</span> O zakono avilo saxke te kerdion mai but
shipki. Numa kotse kai o bezex butilo, o lashimos le Devlesko mai but
butilo.

<span id="an_5:21">5:21</span> Kadia kai o bezex sas katar e martia,
sakadia o lashimos le Devlesko traiil katar o chachimos te ingerel ame
ka traio kai chi mai getolpe katar amaro Del O Jesus Kristo.

<span id="an_6:1">6:1</span> So te mothas? Beshas ando bezex, saxke te
bariol o lashimos le Devlesko?

<span id="an_6:2">6:2</span> Nichi, vov si, ame kai muliam le bezexeske
sar sai mai traiisaras ando bezex?

<span id="an_6:3">6:3</span> Pate, chi zhanen, ke ame savorhe sama bolde
ando Jesus Kristo, samas bolde ande leski martia?

<span id="an_6:4">6:4</span> Samas vusharade lesa ando bolimos leska
martiako, saxke sar o Kristo zhuvindisailo mashkar le mule katar o
barimos le Dadesko, sakadia iame phiras andek nevo traio.

<span id="an_6:5">6:5</span> Ke te samas chidine andek than lesa ande
iek martia, avasa, saikfialo chidine lesa andek zhuvindimos saikfialo ke
sar lesko.

<span id="an_6:6">6:6</span> Ai zhanas mishto, ke amaro phurano manush
sas karfosardo le Kristosa po trushul, saxke amaro stato o bezexalo te
avel mudardo, ai te na mai avas le slugi le bezexeske.

<span id="an_6:7">6:7</span> Ke kodo kai mulo, o bezex ma nai les
putiera.

<span id="an_6:8">6:8</span> Te muliam le Kristosa, ame pachas ame ke
traiisarasa lesa.

<span id="an_6:9">6:9</span> Zhanas ke o Kristo zhuvindisailo andal
mule, ai nashti mai merel; ke e martia ma nai la putiera pe leste.

<span id="an_6:10">6:10</span> Kana mulo, mulo le bezexeske iek data
savorhenge; numa ando traio kai si akana lesko, traiila le Devleske.

<span id="an_6:11">6:11</span> Ai vi tume jinen tume sar mule le
bezexeske, ai zhuvindin le Devleske andek than le Jesus Kristosa.

<span id="an_6:12">6:12</span> No o bezex chi mai trobul te poronchil pe
tumaro stato , kai sai merel te kerel tuke so si drago le statosko.

<span id="an_6:13">6:13</span> Na mai thon kanchi anda tumaro stato te
kerel buchi le bezexeske sar strumento te kerel o nasulimos. Numa den
tume le Devleske, sar manush kai sas andine katar e martia ka traio, ai
den tume antrego te keren leski buchi sar strumenturia te keren so si
vorta.

<span id="an_6:14">6:14</span> Ke o bezex nashti mai poronchil pe
tumende; ke chi traiin tela zakono, numa tela lashimos le Devlesko.

<span id="an_6:15">6:15</span> Apo? Si te keras bezexa, ke chi sam tela
zakono, numa tela lashimos le Devlesko?

<span id="an_6:16">6:16</span> Nichi, Vov si! Zhanen mishto te thona
tume te keren buchi vari kaske ai te pachan lesko mui, tume kerdion le
slugi kodole gazdaski kai keren leste buchi, vai le bezexeske, kai
angerel kai martia, vai te pachan o mui, ai kodia angerel andek traio
vorta angla Del.

<span id="an_6:17">6:17</span> Numa luvudime te avel O Del! Tume kai
sanas mai anglal slugi le bezexeske; pachaian tume akana sa tumare ilesa
ka zakono kai ande kodo sanas sicharde.

<span id="an_6:18">6:18</span> Skepisarde san anda bezex, ai akana san
le slugi le chache zakonosko.

<span id="an_6:19">6:19</span> Dav duma kadia sar iek manush ke pala
kovlimos tumare statosko. Sakadia kai dianas tumaro stato sar sluga le
bi vuzhimaske ai le nasulimaske te traiin ande bezex; sakadia akana thon
tume antrego sar slugi te keren buchi le chache zakonoske, ai te traiin
sar vuzhe.

<span id="an_6:20">6:20</span> Kana sanas le slugi le bezexeske, chi
poronchilas pe tumende o chachimos.

<span id="an_6:21">6:21</span> So nirinas kai kerenas kasavendar dieli
kai akana lazhav tumenge? Kodola dieli angerenas ka martia.

<span id="an_6:22">6:22</span> Numa akana skepime san katar o bezex, ai
aven slugi le Devleske te keren leski buchi; akana nirin kai san phirade
andek traio Swunto, ai te avel tume ando gor o traio kai chi mai
getolpe.

<span id="an_6:23">6:23</span> Ke e pochin le bezexeski si e martia;
numa e podarka le Devleski kai si dini ivia si o traio kai chi mai
getolpe le Jesus Kristosa amaro Del.

<span id="an_7:1">7:1</span> Murhe phral, zhanen vunzhe so si te motav
tumenge ke zhanen o zakono. O zakono si les putiera pek manush zhi ka
traiil.

<span id="an_7:2">7:2</span> Ke iek zhuvli kai si ansurime, phangli la
katar o zakono peske rhomesa zhi kai godi traiil lako rhom; numa te
merela lako rhom skepime la anda zakono kai phandelas la lesa.

<span id="an_7:3">7:3</span> Numa te kerdiola e rhomni avre manusheski,
ai lako rhom inker zhuvindo lo, kodo bushol kurvimos; numa te merela
lako rhom, skepime la katar o zakono, ai sai kerdiol e rhomni avre
manusheski bi te avel kurvia.

<span id="an_7:4">7:4</span> Sakadia tumenge, murhe phral. Tume san mule
le zakonoske kai san andek than chidine ka stato le Kristosko; ai te
aven avresko, tume san akana kodoleske kai sas zhuvindime mashkar le
mule, saxke te keras lashe dieli le Devleske.

<span id="an_7:5">7:5</span> Chaches kana traiisarasas pala amaro stato,
le chorhe dieli, kai o zakono rimolas, kerdionas ande sa amaro stato, ai
angerenas ame kai martia.

<span id="an_7:6">7:6</span> Numa akana skepime sam katar o zakono, ke
muliam kal dieli kai ankerenas ame phangle; akana sai keras buchi le
Devleski aver fielo tela putiera le Swuntone Duxoski, ai na mai sar mai
anglal telai puiera le zakonoske kai sas ramome.

<span id="an_7:7">7:7</span> Apo so mothas? Ke o zakono bezex si? Nichi,
Vov si! Numa o zakono kerdia ma te zhanav so si o bezex. Ke nas te
zhanav ke nai mishto te mangav so si avres, te na phendino mange o
zakono, "Te na mangav so si avres."

<span id="an_7:8">7:8</span> O bezex dabai astardia te kerel ande mande
katar o zakono, but dieli chorhe kai keren ma te mangav so si avres.

<span id="an_7:9">7:9</span> ke bi le zakonosko o bezex nulo lo. Mai
anglal bi le zakonosko traiivas; numa kana avilo o zakono, o bezex
zhuvindisailo, ai me mulem.

<span id="an_7:10">7:10</span> O zakono, kai trobulas te ingerel ka
traio, ingerdia man kai martia.

<span id="an_7:11">7:11</span> Ke o bezex dabai astardia, kerdia te
shubiv ma le zakonosa, ai kerdia te merav.

<span id="an_7:12">7:12</span> O zakono Swunto lo, ai vorta, ai lasho.

<span id="an_7:13">7:13</span> Apo so si lasho kerdilo antunchi martia
mange? Nichi, Vov si! Pala bezex si, o baio ke si kadia, kadia vorta sar
si o bezex. Lia o lashimos te mudarel ma, ai kadia o bezex kerdilo pala
zakono defial nasulimos.

<span id="an_7:14">7:14</span> Zhanas ke o zakono katar O Del si; Numa
me sim stato, bichindo le bezexeske.

<span id="an_7:15">7:15</span> Ke chi zhanav so kerav; chi kerav so
mangav, ai kerav so chi mangav.

<span id="an_7:16">7:16</span> Kana kerav so chi mangav, ai haliarav
kadia ke o zakono lasho lo.

<span id="an_7:17">7:17</span> Ai akana chi sim me kai kerav kodia, numa
o bezex kai si ande mande.

<span id="an_7:18">7:18</span> Zhanav ke so si lasho nai ande mande, nai
ande murho stato. Me mangav, numa nai ma e putiera te kerav o mishtimos.

<span id="an_7:19">7:19</span> Ke chi kerav o mishtimos kai mangav, numa
kerav o nasulimos kai chi mangav.

<span id="an_7:20">7:20</span> Ai te kerava so chi mangav te kerav, chi
sim me kai kerav, kodo si o bezex kai si ande mande.

<span id="an_7:21">7:21</span> No arakhav ande mande kado zakono, kana
mangav te kerav o mishtimos, o nasulimos astardiol mandar.

<span id="an_7:22">7:22</span> Ke voliv o zakono le Devlesko ande murho
ilo.

<span id="an_7:23">7:23</span> Numa dikhav ande murho stato aver zakono,
kai marelpe kodole zakonosa kai murhi goji aliarel ke mishto. Kerel te
astardiuav ka zakono le bezexesko kai si ande murho stato.

<span id="an_7:24">7:24</span> Che chinuime manush sim! Kon skepila ma
anda kado stato kai ingerel ma kai martia?

<span id="an_7:25">7:25</span> O naisimos te avel le Devleske katar O
Jesus Kristo amaro Del! Kadia sai kerav buchi le zakonoski kai si le
Devlesko murha gojasa, numa murho stato kerel buchi le zakonoske, o
zakono le bezexesko.

<span id="an_8:1">8:1</span> Akana ma nai chi iek kris pe kodola kai
traiin le Jesus Kristosa, kai chi phiren na pala stato, numa pala Swunto
Duxo.

<span id="an_8:2">8:2</span> Ke o zakono le Swuntone Duxosko kai del o
traio ando Jesus Kristo, skepisardia ma anda zakono le bezexesko ai
katar e martia.

<span id="an_8:3">8:3</span> O Del kerdia so o zakono le Mosesosko
nashti kerelas, ke o stato le manushesko nai zuralo. Doshardia le
bezexes kai si ando stato le manushesko kana tradia peske shaves
saikfialo sar andek stato kai si sar o bezex le manushesko te ankalavel
o bezex.

<span id="an_8:4">8:4</span> Ai O Del kerdia kodia saxke e kris le
zakonoski te kerdiol anda amende kai phiras na pala stato, numa pala
Swunto Duxo.

<span id="an_8:5">8:5</span> Ke kodola kai traiin pala stato, roden le
dieli kai mangel o stato. Numa kodola kay traiin pala Swunto Duxo lenpe
pala so mangel o Swunto Duxo.

<span id="an_8:6">8:6</span> Te lesa tu pala le dieli kai mangel o stato
kodia angerel kai martia; numa te lesa tu pala so mangel o Swunto Duxo
kodia angerel ando traio ai kai pacha.

<span id="an_8:7">8:7</span> Ke kodola kai lenpe pala le dieli le
statoske, won si le duzhmaia le Devleske; ke chi lenpe pala zakono le
Devlesko, ai vi nashtin.

<span id="an_8:8">8:8</span> Kodola kai traiin le statoske nashtin te
aven drago le Devleske.

<span id="an_8:9">8:9</span> Numa tume chi traiin le statoske, numa
traiin pala Swunto Duxo, ke o Swunto Duxo le Devlesko traiil ande
tumende. Kodo kai nai o Swunto Duxo le Kristosko ande leste, nai lesko.

<span id="an_8:10">8:10</span> Te si o Kristo ande tumende, marka ke
tumaro stato mulo lo pala bezex, o Swunto Duxo si traio ande tumende ke
O Del kerdia anda tumende te aven vorta angla leste.

<span id="an_8:11">8:11</span> Te si o Swunto Duxo le Devlesko, kai
zhuvindisardia le Kristos andai martia ai andia les ka traio, te si ke
traiil vi ande tumende, dela vi o traio ka tumare staturia la phuviake
peske Swuntone Duxosa kai traiil ande tumende.

<span id="an_8:12">8:12</span> Murhe phral, chi mangas kanchi le
statoske te keras so mangel amendar.

<span id="an_8:13">8:13</span> Ke te traiina le statoske, si te meren;
numa le Swuntone Duxosa te mudarena so mangel o stato, traiina.

<span id="an_8:14">8:14</span> Sa kodola kai lenpe pala Swunto Duxo le
Devlesko si shave Devleske.

<span id="an_8:15">8:15</span> Ke o Swunto Duxo kai sas tume dino nai
iek duxo kai inkerel tume sar rhobuvria ai te thol pale e dar ande
tumende; numa kado Swunto Duxo kerel anda tumende shave le Devleske, ai
kai kerel ame te tsipisaras po Del ai te mothas leske, "Dat! Murho Dat!"

<span id="an_8:16">8:16</span> O Swunto Duxo le Devlesko mothol amare
Duxoske ke shave Devleske sam.

<span id="an_8:17">8:17</span> No te sam leske shave, liam ame avela
dino o lashimos le Devlesko, kai O Del shinadia peske narodoske, liam
ame avela dino le Kristosa; ke te chinuisarasa lesa, avasa lesa
luvudime.

<span id="an_8:18">8:18</span> Gindiv ke o chino kai dikhas akana
nashtil te avel iekfialo ke sar o luvudimos le Devlesko kai O Del
sikavela amenge.

<span id="an_8:19">8:19</span> Sai e lumia azhukerel sar mai sigo e
vriama kai O Del sikavela peske shaven.

<span id="an_8:20">8:20</span> Ke e lumia sas thodini kal dieli kai chi
mon kanch, na ke won mangle, numa ke O Del manglia kadia. Numa sai
azhukeren vari so.

<span id="an_8:21">8:21</span> Kodia si ke e lumia avela skepime andek
dies katar e putiera le nasulimaski kai ankerel le, ai vi won avela len
o skepimos sar le shave le Devleske.

<span id="an_8:22">8:22</span> Zhanas ke akana e lumia inker tsipil ai
chinuil sar iek zhuvli kana si la glata.

<span id="an_8:23">8:23</span> Numa na ferdi e lumia; ame kai si ame
vunzhe O Swunto Duxo sar o pervo andal podarki le Devleski, iame
suspinisaras andral zhi kai azhukeras te kerel O Del peske shave anda
amende, ai te ankalavel amaro stato anda bezex.

<span id="an_8:24">8:24</span> Ke O Del skepisardia ame; numa inker
azhukeras te dikhasa so azhukeras; ma nai so azhukeras; savo mai
azhukerel so vunzhi?

<span id="an_8:25">8:25</span> Numa te azhukerasa so chi dikhas,
azhukeras vriamasa.

<span id="an_8:26">8:26</span> Sakadia o Swunto Duxo avel te zhutil ame,
ame kai sam kovle. Ke chi zhanas te rhugisavas sar trobul pe; Numa O
Swunto Duxo rhugilpe ka Del amenge, tsipilimasa kai nashti phenas le
vorbensa.

<span id="an_8:27">8:27</span> Ai O Del, kai dikhel andel ile, aliarel
so mangel O Swunto Duxo; ke O Swunto Duxo rhugilpe anda kodola kai si le
Devleske sar O Del mangel.

<span id="an_8:28">8:28</span> Zhanas ke O Del kerel buchi ande soste
godi po mishtimos kodolenge kai drago le Devles , kodola kai akhardia le
te keren so mangel.

<span id="an_8:29">8:29</span> Ke kodola kai O Del alosardia le mai
anglal manglia vi mai anglal te miazon sar lesko shav, saxke lesko shav
te avel o mai baro bute phralengo.

<span id="an_8:30">8:30</span> Kodolenge kai O Del mai anglal manglia
kadia; vi akhardia le kodolen kai akhardia, vi kerdia anda lende vorta
angla leste; anda kodola kai kerdia vorta vi dia le te aven luvudime
lesa.

<span id="an_8:31">8:31</span> So te mothas mai but? Te si O Del amensa,
kon sai avel pe amende?

<span id="an_8:32">8:32</span> Wo kai chi spasaisardia peske shaves,
numa dia les amenge savorhenge, sar te na del ame vi le kolaver dieli
lesa?

<span id="an_8:33">8:33</span> Kon thola dosh pe kodola kai O Del
alosardia?

<span id="an_8:34">8:34</span> Khonik ke O Del mothol ke nai doshale!
Kon sai dosharel antunchi? Khonik ke O Jesus Kristo si kodo kai mulo,
inker mai but zhuvindisailo, pe chachi rik le Devleski lo, ai rhugilpe
anda amende!

<span id="an_8:35">8:35</span> Kon sai duriarel ame katar e dragostia le
Kristoski? o chino sai dashtil, vai o nekazo, vai te chinuin ame, vai e
bokh, o chorimos, e dar, vai e martia?

<span id="an_8:36">8:36</span> Ke E Vorba le Devleske mothol, "Pala tute
sam thodine kai martia antrego dies; ai keren amensa sar le bakriorhansa
kai angeren le kamasari." (Ps 44:22).

<span id="an_8:37">8:37</span> Numa ande sa kadala dieli sam mai but ke
sar zurale ande kodo kai manglia amen!

<span id="an_8:38">8:38</span> Ke pachav ma ke kanchi nashtil te
duriarel amen katar e dragostia le Devleski; chi e martia, chi o traio;
chi le angeluria, chi iek aver zor, vai putiera chereske; chi so si
akana ai chi so avel;

<span id="an_8:39">8:39</span> chi e zor kai si opre, chi e zor kai si
tele - ai chi iek aver diela kai si, kanch shoxar nashtila te duriarel
ame katar e dragostia le Devleski kai dia ame O Del ando Jesus Kristo
amaro Del.

<span id="an_9:1">9:1</span> O chachimos phenav, le Kristosko sim ai chi
xoxavav, ke murho ilo pherdo lo katar o Swunto Duxo, ai mothol mange ke
o chachimos si.

<span id="an_9:2">9:2</span> Baro nekazo si ma, ai ande murho ilo sagda
iek nekazo si ma pala murho narodoske.

