chi lelpe pala zakono kai meklia O Del: ai kodola kai chi lenpe pala
zakono anena e kris pe pende.

<span id="an_13:3">13:3</span> Chi trobul te daral pe katar le bare kai
poronchin kana le manush keren mishto, numa katar kodola kai keren o
nasulimos. Manges te na daras katar o zhandari? Apo, antunchi ker o
mishtimos, ai mothona mishtimos pa tute.

<span id="an_13:4">13:4</span> Ke wo kerel buchi le Devleski te kerel tu
te keres o mishtimos. Numa te keresa o nasulimos, trobul te daras; ke
nai intaino kai si les e putiera te kerel tu te pochines o nasulimos kai
kerdian: ke wo kerel buchi le Devleske te sikavel e xoli le Devleski
kana kerel te pochinel kodo kai kerdia o nasulimos.

<span id="an_13:5">13:5</span> Anda kodia trobul te les tu pala zakono
le barenge ande cho them, na ferdi te na avel e xoli le Devleske pe
tute, numa ke chi goji trobul te kerel kadia.

<span id="an_13:6">13:6</span> Anda kodia tume pochinen taksa, ke le
manush kai chiden le love keren buchi le Devleske te keren vorta kodia
buchi.

<span id="an_13:7">13:7</span> Pochinen savorhenge so kamen lenge,
pochinen so kamen kodolenge so trobul te pochinen, ai pochinen le love
pe tumari phuv kodoleske kai trobul te avel pochindo, sikaven ke lazhan
katar kodo kai kamen leske, ai keren vorta kodolesa kai trobul te keren
vorta.

<span id="an_13:8">13:8</span> Na kamen love kanikaske, de ferdi te aven
drago iek kavreske. Ke kodo kai si leske drago le kolaver, kodo kerdia o
zakono.

<span id="an_13:9">13:9</span> Ke o zakono si, "Te na keres kurvia; te
na mudares; te na chores; ai na pupuin, ai na mang so si avresko" Kadia
diela ai le kolaver si sa iek zakono, "Te avel tuke drago cho vortako
sar san tu drago tuke."

<span id="an_13:10">13:10</span> E dragostia chi kerel vov si nasulimos
le vortakoske. Kana si amenge drago le kolaver kadia si kai keras sa o
zakono.

<span id="an_13:11">13:11</span> No keren kadia ke zhanen ande che
vriama sam, avili e vriama te pominin tume anda tumaro sovimos. Ke o
skepimos mai pasha amende lo akana de sar kana pachaiam ame e pervo
data.

<span id="an_13:12">13:12</span> E riat pashte nakhli, o dies si te
phuterdiol. Mek te shudas pa amende le dieli kai keren o tuniariko, ai
las pe amende le dieli le vediarike.

<span id="an_13:13">13:13</span> Phiras vorta, sar trobul ande vediara
le dieseski; arakhas ame katar le chingara ai katar o pimos, ai katar le
dieli le bi vuzhe ai katar e kurvia, na maras ame ai te na aven
zhaluzuria vai te na mangen so si avres.

<span id="an_13:14">13:14</span> Numa len pe tumende o nevo traio kai si
ando Jesus Kristo O Del, ai na mai len tume pala tumaro stato, te keren
so wo mangel.

<span id="an_14:1">14:1</span> Len tumensa kodoles kai nai les baro
pachamos, ai na xan tume lesa pe so gindil wo.

<span id="an_14:2">14:2</span> Iek manush gindil ke sai xal swako fielo,
ai aver manush, kai nai les baro pachamos, xal ferdi legumi.

<span id="an_14:3">14:3</span> Kodo kai xal anda swako fielo te na
xoliavol pe kodo kai chi xal uni dieli; ai kodo kai chi xal uni dieli
chi trobul te dosharel kodoles kai xal swako fielo; ke O Del lia les
peste.

<span id="an_14:4">14:4</span> Kon san tu te doshares avreska sluga? Te
kerela peski buchi vorta vai nichi. Kodia zhanela lesko gazda so kerela
lesa. Numa beshela vorta, ke O Del si les e putiera te del les zor.

<span id="an_14:5">14:5</span> Uni gindin ke uni dies mai bare le sar
aver dies, numa uni gindin ke sa le dies iek fielo le. Swako trobul te
pachalpe zurales ande so gindil.

<span id="an_14:6">14:6</span> Kodo kai si leske bari diela o dies,
kerel kodia te luvudil le Devles; kodo kai xal swako fielo kerel kodia
te luvudil le Devles, ke naisil le Devles anda pesko xabe. Kodo kai chi
xal anda swako fielo kerel kodia te luvudil le Devles, ai naisil le
Devles.

<span id="an_14:7">14:7</span> Swako anda amende traiil peske, ai khonik
chi merel peske; Te traiisaras, traiisaras le Devleske, ai te merasa,
meras le Devleske. No te traiisarasa vai te merasa, sa ame Devleske sam.

<span id="an_14:9">14:9</span> Ke o Kristo mulo ai avilo palpale ka
traio te avel O Del le mulengo ai zhuvindengo.

<span id="an_14:10">14:10</span> Numa tu - Sostar doshares che phrales?
Ai tu - gratsia tuke cho phral? Ke savorhe avasa angla Del, te kerel
kris pe amende wo.

<span id="an_14:11">14:11</span> Ke si ramome ande Vorba le Devleski,
"Chaches traiiv, mothol O Del, ai swako manush dela changa angla mande,
ai swako manush phenela ke me sim O Del."

<span id="an_14:12">14:12</span> No swako anda amende trboula te avel
angla Del ai te mothol pa peste.

<span id="an_14:13">14:13</span> Na mai dosharas iek kavres; ai mai bini
den tume goji, te nai keren so nai vorta kai sai rimol tumare phrales,
ai te perel ando bezex.

<span id="an_14:14">14:14</span> Me zhanav, ai pachav ke kadia si katar
O Del O Jesus, ke kanchi nai bi vuzho wo korkorho, numa te gindila vari
kon ke iek diela bi vuzhi la, kodia diela kerdiol bi vuzhi leske.

<span id="an_14:15">14:15</span> Te nekezhisas chi phrales pala iek
diela kai xas, antunchi chi mai phires ande dragostia, na xasar kodoles
kai o Kristo mulo pala leste, pala xaben kai xas!

<span id="an_14:16">14:16</span> So si tumenge lasho chi trobul kodia
diela avrenge te mothon nasulimos pa late.

<span id="an_14:17">14:17</span> Ke o rhaio le Devlesko nai o xaben ai o
pimos; numa so si vorta, ai e pacha, ai o raduimos kai del o Swunto
Duxo.

<span id="an_14:18">14:18</span> Kodo kai kerel buchi le Kristoske kadia
drago lo le Devleske, ai le manush mothon leske kai vorta kerel.

<span id="an_14:19">14:19</span> Rodas le dieli kai anen e pacha, ai so
zuralel ame savorhen ando pachamos.

<span id="an_14:20">14:20</span> Na rimosar e buchi le Devleski pala
xaben. Ke sa le xabenata sai xanpe, numa nai mishto te xas vari so kai
kerel che phrales te perel ando bezez.

<span id="an_14:21">14:21</span> So si mishto si te na xas mas, ai te na
pes mol, ai mekes kadala dieli, te sai rimolpe cho phral pala lende, vai
te kovliarel les. Si tu pachamos?

<span id="an_14:22">14:22</span> So haliares tu korkorho pa kodia diela
garav tuke ai angla Del. Raduime lo kodo kai chi haliarel pe doshalo
kana mangel te kerel iek diela!

<span id="an_14:23">14:23</span> Numa kodo kai chi zhanel te si vorta
vai nichi te xal iek diela, doshalo lo katar O Del te xala. Ke chi kerel
kodia diela peske pachamasa. Ai so godi diela kai keres kai chi avel
katar o pachamos bezex si.

<span id="an_15:1">15:1</span> Ame kai sam zurale ando pachamos trobul
te zhutisaras kodolen kai nai zurale ando pachamos, ai te zhutisaras le
kana si kovle. Ai te na rodas so plachal ame.

<span id="an_15:2">15:2</span> Trobul swako anda amende te rodel te avel
drago peske vortakoske, pe lesko mishtimos ai te bariol ando pachamos.

<span id="an_15:3">15:3</span> Ke O Kristo chi rodelas kon plachal les
numa sar mothol E Vorba le Devleski, "Le dieli le chorhe kodolenge kai
marenas mui lestar pele pe leste."

<span id="an_15:4">15:4</span> So godi sas ramome mai anglal si te
sicharel amen te avel ame e rhavda, ai zor kai del E Vorba le Devleske
te sai avel ame ando ilo kodo pachamos te azhukeras.

<span id="an_15:5">15:5</span> O Del kai lestar avel e rhavda ai e zor,
kerel te sai traiin andek than iek kavresa sar sas o Kristo Jesus.

<span id="an_15:6">15:6</span> Saxke savorhe andek than, ai ande iek
glaso luvudin le Devles, o Dat amare Devlesko O Jesus Kristo.

<span id="an_15:7">15:7</span> Premin iek kavres, sar o Kristo
premisardia tumen ando barimos le Devlesko.

<span id="an_15:8">15:8</span> Akana phenav tumenge ke o Kristo kerdilo
e sluga le Zhidovongi te kerel le shinaimata kai O Del kerdia lenge
dadange, ai te sikavel ke O Del kerel so mothol,

<span id="an_15:9">15:9</span> Avilo saxke vi kodola kai Nai Zhiduvuria
luvudin le Devles pala pesko lashimos. E Vorba le Devleske mothol, "Anda
kodia luvudiva tu mashkar le thema, ai jilabava ande cho anav."

<span id="an_15:10">15:10</span> Ai mai mothol E Vorba le Devleske,
"Tume kai Nai Zhiduvuria, raduin tume leske narodosa, kai O Del
alosardia!"

<span id="an_15:11">15:11</span> Ai mai mothol, "Naisin le Devleske ai
luvudin le Devles, tume kai chi san Zhidovon, ai sa o narodo te luvudil
le Devles!"

<span id="an_15:12">15:12</span> Ai o Isaiah mai mothol, "O shav le
Jessesko avela; ai tholape te poronchil pel Nai Zhiduvuria, ai le Nai
Zhiduvuria pachanape ande leste."

<span id="an_15:13">15:13</span> O Del kai del e rhavda, te pherel tume
raduimos ai pacha vorta ando pachamos kai si tume ande leste, saxke te
aven barvale ande rhavda katar e putiera le Swuntone Duxoski.

<span id="an_15:14">15:14</span> Murhe phral: zhanav ke pherdo lashimos
san, pherdo zhanglimos san, ai sai sicharen iek kavres.

<span id="an_15:15">15:15</span> Numa tromailem te ramov tumenge ai ande
murho lil ande but thana, ramosardem tumenge te seren tume so vunzhe
sichilian. Ramosardem tumenge kadia pala lashimos kai dia ma O Del.

<span id="an_15:16">15:16</span> Te avav ek pasturi le Kristosko le
narodoske kai Nai Zhiduvuria, ai kadia kerav iek buchi swunto kai
angerav e lashi viasta le Devleski, saxke kodola manush kai Nai
Zhiduvuria aven lashe le Devleske, ai sai aven leske katar o Swunto
Duxo.

<span id="an_15:17">15:17</span> Andek than le Kristosa sai luvudiv ma
ande buchi kai kerav le Devleske.

<span id="an_15:18">15:18</span> Ke chi tromailemas te mothav chi iek
diela kai o Kristo chi kerdia mansa, te anav kodolen kai Nai Zhiduvuria
te pachanpe ando Del, numa peska vorbasa ai so kerdia.

<span id="an_15:19">15:19</span> Palai putiera le semnongi ai le
miraklongi, ai katar e putiera le Swuntone Duxoski, o Duxo le Devlesko;
kadia de andai Jerusalem, ai le thema kai sas pashe zhi ande Illiricum,
phendem e lashi viasta le Kristoski.

<span id="an_15:20">15:20</span> Drago sas mange te mothav e viasta le
Kristoski, kotse kai chi ashunde pa Kristo, saxke te na kerav khangeri
kotse kai kerdia aver.

<span id="an_15:21">15:21</span> Sar ramol E Vorba le Devleske,
"Kodolenge kai chi phende pa Kristo, dikhena, ai kodola kai chi ashunde
pa leste, haliarena."

<span id="an_15:22">15:22</span> Kodia aterdiardia ma butivar te zhav
tumende.

<span id="an_15:23">15:23</span> Numa akana getosardem murhi buchi katse
kai si ande kadala thema, ai de but bersh manglem te dikhav tume;

<span id="an_15:24">15:24</span> Ai mangav te dikhav tume kana avava
ande Shpania, avav tumende; ke mangav te dikhav tume kana nakhava
kotsar, kana beshava tumensa xantsi vriama mai anglal, sai zhutin ma te
zhav ande Shpania,

<span id="an_15:25">15:25</span> Numa akana zhav ande Jerusalem te kerav
buchi le Devleski mashkar le shave le Devleske kai si kotse.

<span id="an_15:26">15:26</span> Ke le shave le Devleske andai Macedonia
ai andai Gretsia magle te chiden love le chorhenge kai si anda narodo le
Devlesko ande Jerusalem.

<span id="an_15:27">15:27</span> Won mangle te keren kodia; numa chaches
trobulas te keren kodole chorhenge kadia diela, ke le shave le Devleske
le Zhiduvuria andai Jerusalem vulade pengo mishtimos kai dia le O Del
kodolensa kai Nai Zhiduvuria, No kodola kai Nai Zhiduvuria trobul vi won
te zhutin le ai te den le so trobul le katse pe phuv.

<span id="an_15:28">15:28</span> Kana getova kadia buchi ai dava le le
love kai chide lenge, zhavatar ande Shpania ai nakhava tumendar kana
zhava kotse.

<span id="an_15:29">15:29</span> Ai zhanav ke kana zhava tumende, avava
le lashimasa katar o Kristo.

<span id="an_15:30">15:30</span> Numa eta so mangav tumendar, murhe
phral, katar amaro Del O Jesus Kristo, ai katar e dragostia kai del O
Swunto Duxo: maren tume mansa ando rhugimos ka Del mange:

<span id="an_15:31">15:31</span> Rhugin tume saxke te skepiv katar
kodola kai chi pachanpe ando Del kai si ande Judea, ai o zhutimos kai
anav ando Jerusalem te avel mishto chetaiime kotse mashkar o narodo le
Devleske.

<span id="an_15:32">15:32</span> Kadia aresava tumende pherdo raduimos
te mangela O Del, ai arakhava pacha mashkar tumende.

<span id="an_15:33">15:33</span> O Del kai del e pacha te avel tumensa
savorhensa. Amen.

<span id="an_16:1">16:1</span> Tradav tumenge amare phei e Phoebe, kai
kerel buchi ande khangeri ando Cencheae.

<span id="an_16:2">16:2</span> Premin la ando anav le Devlesko, sar
kerel pe mashkar o narodo le Devlesko, ai zhutin la ande soste godi kai
trobula la te zhutin la; woi zhutisardia bute narodos vi man, ai
zhutisardia but.

<span id="an_16:3">16:3</span> Roden ai dikhen le Priscilla ai Aquila,
won kerde buchi mansa ande buchi le Jesus Kristoski.

<span id="an_16:4">16:4</span> Won thode pengo traio te skepin murho,
chi naisiv lenge - ferdi me, numa sa le khangeria kodolenge kai Nai
Zhiduvuria ande lumia naisin lenge.

<span id="an_16:5">16:5</span> Ai dikhen vi e khangeri kai chidelpe ande
lengo kher. Dikhen vi murhe vortakos o Epenetus, kai sas o pervo kai
pachaiape ando Kristo ande Asia.

<span id="an_16:6">16:6</span> Dikhen vi la Maria, kai kerdia but buchi
tumenge.

<span id="an_16:7">16:7</span> Dikhen o Andronicus ai o Junias, kai si
murhe niamuria ai vi won sas ande temnitsa mansa. Won mishto chetaiimele
mashkar le apostluria; inker mai anglal mandar dine sas pe ka Del.

<span id="an_16:8">16:8</span> Dikhen o Ampliatus, murho lasho vortako
ando Del.

<span id="an_16:9">16:9</span> Dikhen le Urbanus, amaro zhutitori ande
buchi le Kristoski, ai o Stachys kai si mange drago.

<span id="an_16:10">16:10</span> Dikhen le Apelles kai sikadia pesko
pachamos ando Krsto. Dikhen le narodos kai si anda kher kodoleske kai
bushol Aristobulus.

<span id="an_16:11">16:11</span> Dikhen o Herodion murho niamos, dikhen
le narodos anda kher le Narcissus kai pachanpe ando Del.

<span id="an_16:12">16:12</span> Dikhen o Tryphaena ai o Tryphosa kai
keren buchi le Devleski, ai murhi kuchi Persis kai kerdia but buchi
leske,

<span id="an_16:13">16:13</span> Dikhen o rufus, kai si ek lasho
servatori le Devlesko, ai leske dei, kai si i mange sar iek dei.

<span id="an_16:14">16:14</span> Dikhen o Asyncritus, o Phlegon, o
Hermes, o Patrobas, o Hermas, ai le kolavre phralen kai si lensa.

<span id="an_16:15">16:15</span> Dikhen o Philologus, ai e Julia, o
Nereus, ai leski phei, o Olimpas, ai sa le shave le Devleske kai si
lensa.

<span id="an_16:16">16:16</span> Dikhen tume iek kavres ai chumiden tume
pe buka sar phral. Sa le khangeria le Kristoske traden tumenge but bax,
zor ai sastimos.

<span id="an_16:17">16:17</span> Mangav tumendar, murhe phral: arakhen
tume katar kodola kai rimon ai xasaren kodolen kai pachanpe ando Del,
kai mothon ke nai vorta o zakono kai sicharde tume; durion lendar.

<span id="an_16:18">16:18</span> Ke kasavestar narodo chi keren buchi le
Kristoski amaro Del, numa penge jieske; Ai andel vorbi le shukar kai
mothon, ai lenge divanuria le barimatange atsaven le ile le manushenge
kai si proste.

<span id="an_16:19">16:19</span> Sa e lumia zhanel ke pachan o mui le
Devlesko, raduima anda tumende: Numa mangav te aven gojaver saxke te
keren o lashimos. Ai vuzhe te na keren o nasulimos.

<span id="an_16:20">16:20</span> O Del kai del e pacha, sigo vriama
licharela le benges tela tumare punrhe. Te avel o lashimos amaro
Devlesko O Jesus Kristo tumensa.

<span id="an_16:21">16:21</span> O Timothe, murhe zhutitori ande buchi,
tradel tumenge but bax, zor ai sastimos, ai vi o Lucius, o Jason, ai o
Sosipater, murhe miamuria.

<span id="an_16:22">16:22</span> Ai me, o Tertius, kai ramosardia kado
lil, tradav tumenge but bax, zor ai sastimos ando Del.

<span id="an_16:23">16:23</span> O Gaius, kado kai si mande khere, ai
kai leste chidelpe e khangeri, tradel tumenge but bax, zor ai sastimos;
o Erastus, kai lel sama katar le love le foroske, ai amaro phral o
Quartus, traden tumenge but bax, zor ai sastimos.

<span id="an_16:24">16:24</span> O lashimos amaro Devlesko O Jesus
Kristo te avel tumensa savorhensa. Amen.

<span id="an_16:25">16:25</span> Luvudisaras le Devles! Kai leste si e
putiera te del tume zor ando pachamos, ande lashi viasta kai anav, e
viasta kai phenav pa Jesus Kristo, ai so sichiliam kai sas garado katar
O Del, kadia diela sas garadi but vriama palpale.

<span id="an_16:26">16:26</span> Numa akana kodia diela sas thodi ande
vediara, katar E Vorba le Devleske le profetonge, kai sas dine katar O
Del, kai shoxar chi merela, ai kadia viasta si sa le themenge, saxke te
pachanpe ai te lenpe pala late.

<span id="an_16:27">16:27</span> Ka Del ferdi e goji, te avel o barimos
katar O Jesus Kristo ande swako vriama! Amen.

